1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 5=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=I'll Keep You Safe=

4
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,320
If I kill you

5
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,640
by accident,

6
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:51,320
I could say you were killed

7
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,150
by the poison.

8
00:00:54,670 --> 00:00:55,710
Besides,

9
00:00:56,030 --> 00:00:57,430
the chief is my uncle.

10
00:00:57,750 --> 00:00:58,710
Who do you think

11
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:00,880
he'll help,

12
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:03,000
you or me?

13
00:01:15,070 --> 00:01:16,280
Your Majesty, please don't go.

14
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,130
Let go.

15
00:01:17,140 --> 00:01:18,000
Your Majesty!

16
00:01:18,070 --> 00:01:19,480
If you keep drawing on your power

17
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,790
without the Frost Seal,

18
00:01:20,790 --> 00:01:21,870
your life will be at risk.

19
00:01:22,070 --> 00:01:22,910
By then,

20
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,310
even the Frost Seal

21
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,680
can't help you.

22
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:27,310
(The Goddess's power is unique.)

23
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,240
(I've long suffered from the backlash.)

24
00:01:29,310 --> 00:01:30,790
(Zhaoli took away my Frost Seal.)

25
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,590
(Yet she felt no backlash at all.)

26
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:35,480
(Could she be the Saintess Xihe
I've been looking for?)

27
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,510
I never thought that today,

28
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,710
this humble life of mine

29
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,350
would be of concern to so many.

30
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:44,000
You're indeed humble.

31
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,450
So, what makes you think

32
00:01:45,450 --> 00:01:46,940
Che would care for you?

33
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:49,550
Oh, right.

34
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,840
Isn't your secret lover formidable?

35
00:01:52,150 --> 00:01:53,680
Today, I'll make you understand

36
00:01:53,710 --> 00:01:55,760
that those men's affections
mean nothing.

37
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,710
None of them can protect you.

38
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,760
This is the magical artifact I obtained.

39
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,120
Once it detonates,

40
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:06,040
you'll be slowly consumed by its power;

41
00:02:06,310 --> 00:02:09,080
your organs will fail one after another.

42
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,520
Wu Luoluo,

43
00:02:11,030 --> 00:02:13,030
the harder you try to grasp something,

44
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:15,380
the further it slips from your hands.

45
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:18,000
Even if you kill me,
you'll never have it.

46
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:20,080
Then let's have a try.

47
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,640
You...

48
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,470
Since you're here,

49
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:44,630
let's settle
old and new grudges together.

50
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,630
(He and the husband from my dreams)

51
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,150
(share the same spell.)

52
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:21,710
From this day on,

53
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,520
I'll keep you safe.

54
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,680
How about that?

55
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,120
Your Majesty,

56
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,630
you just humiliated me;

57
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:38,030
now, you want to protect me?

58
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:41,280
What on earth are you doing?

59
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,220
About what happened today,

60
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:45,870
I'm sorry.

61
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:48,310
It won't happen again.

62
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:52,750
I don't believe you anymore.

63
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,360
Ying Du.

64
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:16,550
So cold.

65
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:18,510
The cold poison is acting up.

66
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,480
(Ying Du,)

67
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,950
(without the Frost Seal,)

68
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:24,190
(your power has weakened greatly.)

69
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,680
(I can end you soon)

70
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,800
(and take your place.)

71
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,870
How strange.

72
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,950
Why is his body still so cold?

73
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,640
You're awake.

74
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:29,600
Ying Du,

75
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,610
are you out of your mind?

76
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,800
Why not tend to your wound first?

77
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,160
Once this poison goes into the organs...

78
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,600
That's none of your concern.

79
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,760
Well.

80
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,360
Since you're awake,

81
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,950
leave now.

82
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,680
I knew you wouldn't just watch me die.

83
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,240
I'd save anyone, not just you.

84
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:00,070
I didn't finish talking

85
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:01,360
in the daytime.

86
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,070
What do you mean?

87
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:04,630
You're right.

88
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:07,160
No one has the power
to decide your fate at will.

89
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,160
Though the pain you suffered

90
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,310
was never my intention,

91
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,120
it still happened because of me.

92
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:13,630
I know you don't believe me,

93
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,630
but I still want to tell you this.

94
00:06:17,830 --> 00:06:19,430
When I said I'd protect you,

95
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,600
I meant it.

96
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,630
I wasn't toying with you.

97
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:31,000
The ruler protecting a healer?

98
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,150
I think

99
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:34,070
you want to use me for something.

100
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,630
Here's a deal.

101
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:38,160
(As expected,)

102
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,630
(he wants something from me.)

103
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,240
My power has been acting strangely.

104
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,950
Only when I make contact with you

105
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,800
can I fully wield it.

106
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,270
So, I wish to form a pact with you.

107
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,040
You'll be my link to channel power,

108
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,760
and I

109
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,800
will protect you in return.

110
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:00,710
Of course,

111
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,390
I'll also use the Bracelet

112
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,720
to help you find the one
from your dreams.

113
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,510
Why do you say

114
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,240
you can only use your power

115
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:14,000
when we are in contact?

116
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:17,360
(About our shared fate,)

117
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:19,600
(the fewer who know that, the better.)

118
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:21,240
When you were in the Palace,

119
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,170
we pretended to have consummation.

120
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,160
Somehow,

121
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,680
I transferred my power to you.

122
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,800
So, you came here for this.

123
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,750
Why didn't you say so before?

124
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,560
I didn't want you to misunderstand.

125
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,800
I never meant to keep it from you.

126
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,880
Alright then.

127
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,360
I'll agree to it.

128
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,750
The ruler will safeguard me

129
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,930
and help me find someone.

130
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:47,190
Why would I refuse such a thing?

131
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,630
(Zhaoli,)

132
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,510
(why does he make you feel
so disheartened?)

133
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,390
I did not summon you.

134
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:09,750
Why do you come on your own?

135
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,900
If the ruler were to learn...

136
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,660
With his present condition,

137
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,560
he cannot sense my presence at all.

138
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,510
Besides,

139
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,270
he's not here, isn't he?

140
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:20,040
How dare you bring this up?

141
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,740
You once told me

142
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:23,500
that the healer has a rare constitution

143
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:24,830
and she can ease the ruler's pain

144
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:27,080
from the Frostbite Curse
caused by the Goddess's power.

145
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:28,660
But now, the ruler is bewitched by her

146
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,920
and refuses to return.

147
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,680
Please, calm your anger.

148
00:08:32,550 --> 00:08:34,600
The ruler likely stays there

149
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,000
to reclaim his power.

150
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:39,480
But if that healer

151
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:40,720
were gone,

152
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,960
the ruler's thoughts

153
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:44,600
would return to where they belong.

154
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,240
In that case,

155
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:49,360
end her life.

156
00:08:55,410 --> 00:09:00,060
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

157
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:06,860
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

158
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:11,600
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

159
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:14,500
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

160
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:20,310
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

161
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:24,010
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

162
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,710
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

163
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:30,750
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

164
00:09:30,750 --> 00:09:33,130
♪And that is enough♪

165
00:09:33,130 --> 00:09:36,920
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

166
00:09:37,130 --> 00:09:39,890
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

167
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:46,010
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

